author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the world of Artificial Intelligence and discuss a topic I've seen floating around since it's inception, and that's the concept of inbreeding. How can a set of 1s and 0s become inbred, yes it can and heres how to avoid it. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Is AI Becoming Inbred...
